            {
              "textEn": "<b>Lesson 3 • Discussing a new ad campaign</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "Ted works for an advertising agency. He's presenting to Sam and Lisa, who work for Pacific Beer Company."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Lisa:</b> Ted would like to run some ideas by us for our new ad campaign."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Ted:</b> Please, "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "keep an open mind",
              "word": "keep an open mind",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/k/....mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ". Remember that nothing is set in stone yet. We're still just brainstorming."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Sam:</b> I hope that doesn't mean we're about to hear a lot of"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "half-baked ideas",
              "word": "half-baked ideas",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/h/half-baked-ideas.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn":	"!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Ted:</b> I think you're going to like this. Our idea is to use a black bear as our mascot.* Our"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "tagline",
              "word": "tagline",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/t/tagline.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "can be: \"Strong enough to satisfy a bear.\""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Lisa:</b> It would be great if people would associate our brand with a bear — strong and independent. That would really improve our brand equity."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Sam:</b> I don't want to"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "throw cold water",
              "word": "throw cold water",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/t/throw cold water.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "on your idea, but where did you get the idea for a bear?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Ted:</b> Didn't you hear about that bear at the campground a couple weeks ago? He entered a tent and drank two dozen Pacific beers! What a great endorsement for Pacific beer!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Lisa:</b> I think we're"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "on the right track",
              "word": "on the right track",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/o/on-the-right-track.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "<b>with this campaign. The bear should"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "generate lots of buzz",
              "word": "generate lots of buzz",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/g/generate-buzz.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ". Everybody will be talking about the bear who loves Pacific beer!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Ted:</b> And here's the"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "icing on the cake",
              "word": "icing on the cake",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/i/icing-on-the-cake.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ": he won't demand an arm and a leg to"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "plug product",
              "word": "plug our product",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/p/plug-product.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ". In fact, we can probably pay him in beer!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Sam:</b> Okay, you've"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "twisted my arm",
              "word": "twisted my arm",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/c/....mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": ". Let's"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "run with the idea",
              "word": "run with the idea",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/r/run-.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "textEn": "<b>Ted:</b> Great. I'll"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "flesh it out ",
              "word": "flesh it out ",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/f/flesh-it-out .mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "some more and"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "touch base with",
              "word": "touch base with",
              "wordAudioSrc": "/dictionary/t/touch-base-with.mp3"
            },
            {
              "textEn": "you in a couple of days."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
